":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8nG","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32225,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/16\/salaam-arrives-leaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":32220,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greet with peace arriving and leaving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man passed by the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was sitting in a gathering. The man said, \u201cPeace be upon you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTen good deeds.\u201d Another man passed by, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you and the mercy of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12973,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/salaam-mixed-group-yahud\/","url_meta":{"origin":32220,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting mixed group with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a mixed gathering of Muslims and Jews and he greeted them all with peace. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2702 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0